text: Kjell Rune Flo (born 11 April 1961) is a retired Norwegian football defender. He is a brother of Jostein Flo, Jarle Flo and Tore Andre Flo, and father of Ulrik Flo. He made his debut for Stryn TIL in 1977, and spent his career there until retiring after the 1996 season. The exception was the year 1990, when he played on the first-tier for Molde FK. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:People from Stryn Category:Norwegian footballers Category:Stryn TIL players Category:Molde FK players Category:Eliteserien players Category:Association football defenders
